'''Askira/Uba''' un hukuma pamarun gal diiwal Borno Najeriya hautirde den eɗe ɗer gelle ɗen Askira. Lamba wuro noddirgo go gebbal gal hango wonii 601. Gotun eɗer saraji Askira uban lassa kanjun woni artuɗun sare hesere waɓɓere yawun ɗun ɗun anɗitoya e ɗer yiyam ɓiyi mishan Amurka eɗeɓe garki ɗen goɗɗun kautuɗu yimɓe ɗarnoɓe ko nonii yawii gabbe yawufuɗɗi anɗituki e suduki goɗaki-goɗaki ɗun inɗe lassa virus inare eɗun fuɗɗi wanguki.
E leuru Yulin dundu 2014 woɓɓe ɓe bindiga ɓe ɗun hammoto ɓiɓɓe Boko Haram yari konu e sareji ɗin huyim e dilla gonɗun hukuma pamarun Askira Uba ɗen ɓe paɗɗi yimɓe jewe nayo e sappo e tate e jewetati. Honoɓe ɓen ɓe gurtoika gada ladde sambisa joɗiɓe ɓe ɗun laggoyi eɓe giɗi walle ki gada ardiɓe e yimɓe ɓe risku.
